(102036, 'ruRU', 'So you hunt the Dark Riders as well? Long have I searched for a way to rid Duskwood of their curse, but now it looks like I have become the hunted. \n\nThough we may share an immediate goal, the sins you bear plainly show me that I cannot aid your cause. The Light is not well served by taking power from one evil only to hand it to another.', '', 21154),
