(103308, 'ruRU', '', 'Yeah! Let me think... I heard it back when Uncle Chen and I were still traveling the world before we found the way to Pandaria.$b$bWe were in Booty Bay one night staying at a place called the Salty Sailor. While there I met a giant creature who called himself a Tol''vir.$b$bWe chatted for a long time and he told me of his homeland, a place covered in sands called Uldum.', 21154),
