(108046, 'ruRU', '<Grash frowns.>$b$bMagic stick is very old. Very powerful. It is made of living water.$b$bSnake witch says the magic stick came from her queen. It speaks to the sea. Sea monsters obey the stick. It heals their wounds.$b$bStick fill the heads of giants with dark and pain. The dark comes from the witch, not the stick.', '', 21154),
