(109178, 'ruRU', 'If you had faith in the light, Demon Hunter, there would be nothing to fear!', '', 21154),
(109179, 'ruRU', 'It does not matter what could happen to his reputation. He has already ruined it. This is why you are still an apprentice.', '', 21154),
(109180, 'ruRU', 'But master, this man was innocent! His name was cleared, surely he deserves a second chance?', '', 21154),
(109181, 'ruRU', 'You have done everyone a great service, friend. Give cousin Ly''leth my regards. A good merchant knows how to keep his friends and contacts, just in case they have need of each other.', '', 21154),
(109182, 'ruRU', 'To Shield''s Rest!', '', 21154),
(109183, 'ruRU', 'Make yourself comfortable. It''s a bit of a ride to Stormheim.', '', 21154),
(109184, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Spell_Holy_FistOfJustice:20|t Krosus is about to destroy the bridge with a |cFFFF0404|Hspell:205875|h[Slam]|h|r!', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Spell_Holy_FistOfJustice:20|t Krosus is about to destroy the bridge with a |cFFFF0404|Hspell:205875|h[Slam]|h|r!', 21154),
(109185, 'ruRU', 'My wounds were severe, but $n arrived just in time.', '', 21154),
(109186, 'ruRU', 'The Light has come to vanquish you, demon!', '', 21154),
(109187, 'ruRU', 'Brann introduced me to Prustaga not long ago. That dwarf sure has a way with words... he can even charm a vrykul!', '', 21154),
(109188, 'ruRU', 'This ship''s carrying prisoners! We could use their help, $n. Free them!', '', 21154),
(109189, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Achievement_Boss_YoggSaron_01:20|tA Dominator Tentacle faces you and readies |cFFFF0000|Hspell:208689|h[Ground Slam]|h|r!', '|TInterface\\Icons\\Achievement_Boss_YoggSaron_01:20|tA Dominator Tentacle faces you and readies |cFFFF0000|Hspell:208689|h[Ground Slam]|h|r!', 21154),
(109190, 'ruRU', 'Accordin'' to some ancient texts we translated back in the Explorer''s League, Titanstrike focuses the power of storms into blasts of energy.', '', 21154),
(109191, 'ruRU', 'If that''s true, it could do some serious damage to the Legion. I s''pose we''ll find out ourselves soon enough.', '', 21154),
(109192, 'ruRU', 'Druids of Azeroth, protectors of the Dream, my sons and daughters...', '', 21154),
(109193, 'ruRU', 'I must speak quickly, for my mind grows clouded.', '', 21154),
(109194, 'ruRU', 'When I sensed Shaladrassil''s corruption, I entered the Emerald Dream to destroy the Nightmare''s source.', '', 21154),
(109195, 'ruRU', 'Deeper and deeper I fought. When I arrived at the Rift, I saw their true strength, and my heart filled with horror.', '', 21154),
(109197, 'ruRU', 'The Nightmare will spread like a disease, festering and multiplying. Soon, it will engulf all of Azeroth in its twisted reality.', '', 21154),
(109198, 'ruRU', 'I can no longer see the way back to the Dream. I am trapped here, in a Nightmare of my own making.', '', 21154),
(109199, 'ruRU', 'Druids, my time is done. It is up to you now.', '', 21154),
(109200, 'ruRU', '', 'Taz''dingo! Thank'' ya for getting me out of there!', 21154),
(109201, 'ruRU', 'I''ll introduce ye to Prustaga when yer ready.', '', 21154),
(109202, 'ruRU', '', 'I am Mayla, daughter of Ulan, and I... I stand as Chieftain of the Highmountain Tribes.', 21154),
(109203, 'ruRU', '', 'Don''t worry, they''re friendlier than they look.', 21154),
(109204, 'ruRU', 'I''m glad you heeded our call. We''ve been discussing inviting you into our ranks for some time.', '', 21154),
(109206, 'ruRU', 'None taken... so long as you don''t insult me face.', '', 21154),
(109207, 'ruRU', '', 'I''ve heard quite a bit about your accomplishments. I can''t imagine half of it can possibly be true.', 21154),
(109208, 'ruRU', '', 'It''s good to finally see you again. I miss our adventures together.', 21154),
(109209, 'ruRU', 'Such power! I feel the demon''s essence infusing every fiber of my being!', '', 21154),
(109210, 'ruRU', 'I fear for your soul, Demon Hunter. It''s not too late, you can still turn to the light and let it cleanse you of this corruption.', '', 21154),
(109211, 'ruRU', 'Spare me, paladin. Your people should be well aware what horrors the Burning Legion is capable of.', '', 21154),
(109212, 'ruRU', '', 'Much thanks again, mon, for gettin'' us out of there!', 21154),
(109213, 'ruRU', 'We seek the leader of this den of horrors; an Eredar that goes by the name of Lady Calindris.', '', 21154),
(109214, 'ruRU', '', 'Ay, she be just outside directin'' the felguard ta load up more captives. I be havin'' a score to settle with her so if ya be aimin'' ta take her out, count me in.', 21154),
(109215, 'ruRU', 'Lead on, Farseer, and I shall follow.', '', 21154),
(109216, 'ruRU', 'Come, let''s move before we encounter any further suprises.', '', 21154),
(109217, 'ruRU', 'These are troubling words, Farseer.', '', 21154),
(109218, 'ruRU', 'We must defeat the Twilight''s Hammer and restore balance to Deepholm.', '', 21154),
(109219, 'ruRU', 'The servant of Therazane is bound by the dark powers of the void. I hope we are not too late!', '', 21154),
(109220, 'ruRU', 'The horrors... these fiends must be destroyed.', '', 21154),
(109221, 'ruRU', 'Twilight whelps? I thought the Twilight Dragonflight were extinct...', '', 21154),
(109222, 'ruRU', 'The Fal''dorei have taken everything... from me.', '', 21154),
(109223, 'ruRU', 'I still not stand by and watch as demons tear this world apart.$B$BThe time has come for the nightborne to earn their place on Azeroth.', '', 21154),
(109224, 'ruRU', 'This one is almost lost to the corruption! We must hurry!', '', 21154),
(109225, 'ruRU', 'We have put an end to the rituals, but I fear the worst is yet ahead of us...', '', 21154),
(109226, 'ruRU', 'We should return to Therazane and inform her of what has transpired here.', '', 21154),
(109227, 'ruRU', 'Our prey stands before us! We must strike now, before she can summon her defenses!', '', 21154),
(109228, 'ruRU', 'Join me in raising a glass not only to our newest Shadow, but to the dawn of a new era for the Uncrowned.', '', 21154),
(109229, 'ruRU', 'Something''s off about this here brew...', '', 21154),
(109230, 'ruRU', '', 'Vanessa...?', 21154),
(109231, 'ruRU', 'Today, $p secured the legendary Fangs of the Devourer, and in doing so has enabled us to strike at the Legion directly.', '', 21154),
(109232, 'ruRU', 'Today, $p secured the legendary Kingslayers, and in doing so has enabled us to strike at the Legion directly.', '', 21154),
(109233, 'ruRU', 'Get away from there!', 'Get away from there!', 21154),
(109234, 'ruRU', 'You have come to help Ly''leth destroy our family! Be gone!', 'You have come to help Ly''leth destroy our family! Be gone!', 21154),
(109235, 'ruRU', 'Ngh! Who ARE you?!', 'Ngh! Who ARE you?!', 21154),
(109236, 'ruRU', '', 'Well done!', 21154),
(109237, 'ruRU', 'Just... finish me off.', 'Just... finish me off.', 21154),
(109238, 'ruRU', 'Come with me. Ly''leth wants to speak with you.', 'Come with me. Ly''leth wants to speak with you.', 21154),
(109239, 'ruRU', 'She wants to preach her traitorous ideals to me further? Fine. Let us go.', 'She wants to preach her traitorous ideals to me further? Fine. Let us go.', 21154),
(109240, 'ruRU', '', 'You''re more resilient than I thought. I was hoping to take you somewhere a little less... populated.', 21154),
(109241, 'ruRU', '', 'Come on, show me the ''legendary fighter'' I''ve heard so much about!', 21154),
(109242, 'ruRU', '', 'No! I''ve worked too hard to be undermined by the likes of you!', 21154),
(109243, 'ruRU', '', 'Oh, my head... Valeera, you ok?', 21154),
(109244, 'ruRU', '', 'Valeera nods.', 21154),
(109245, 'ruRU', 'I was not successful in getting the Bloodtotem tribe to help us with this. I hope Jale has enough leverage.', '', 21154),
(109246, 'ruRU', 'I have only just returned from Bloodtotem lands, but I have heard of the aid you lent our people. \n\nIt shames me to see the day when outsiders like yourself are more willing to help us than our fellow tribes.', '', 21154),
(109247, 'ruRU', 'We need your help negotiating with the Underking.', 'We need your help negotiating with the Underking.', 21154),
(109248, 'ruRU', 'Jale wishes to negotiate with these savages? A bold move, though probably a foolish one.', '', 21154),
(109249, 'ruRU', 'By the Earthmother! It is just as a I feared... the Twilight Dragonflight has returned!', '', 21154),
(109250, 'ruRU', 'Take good care of it.', 'Take good care of it.', 21154),
(109251, 'ruRU', 'Don''t get too reckless!', 'Don''t get too reckless!', 21154),
(109252, 'ruRU', 'Bring her back in one piece!', 'Bring her back in one piece!', 21154),
(109253, 'ruRU', '', 'Our work is nearly finished... do not allow these meddling shaman to interfere with the rituals!', 21154),
(109254, 'ruRU', '', 'Find them! Leave no stone unturned!', 21154),
(109255, 'ruRU', '', 'None survive, so says the Grand Magistrix!', 21154),
(109256, 'ruRU', '', 'The Moon Guard are finished! Slay them all.', 21154),
(109257, 'ruRU', '', '|TInterface\\Icons\\inv_feather_05.blp:20|t %s readies |cFFF00000|Hspell:210547|h[Razor Wing]|h|r.', 21154),
(109258, 'ruRU', '', 'Scour the stronghold. None escape alive.', 21154),
(109259, 'ruRU', 'I heard what you did for the Rivermane tribe.$b$bWhen we first met in Dalaran I did not expect that you would be as helpful to us as you have been.$b$bIt is much appreciated.', '', 21154),
(109260, 'ruRU', '', 'Wipe this place clean of their inferior magics. The Moon Guard is finished.', 21154),
(109261, 'ruRU', 'For Nar''thalas!', 'For Nar''thalas!', 21154),
(109262, 'ruRU', 'Drive back the scaled menace!', 'Drive back the scaled menace!', 21154),
(109263, 'ruRU', 'Show the naga no mercy!', 'Show the naga no mercy!', 21154),
(109264, 'ruRU', 'Face the wrath of the Nightwatchers!', 'Face the wrath of the Nightwatchers!', 21154),
(109265, 'ruRU', 'Strike down the naga filth!', 'Strike down the naga filth!', 21154),
(109266, 'ruRU', '', 'Our soldiers grow weary of the naga''s relentless assault. Rally the Nightwatchers, champion, and drive the naga back to the depths where they belong!', 21154),
(109267, 'ruRU', '', 'We appreciate your help, champion. You''ve allowed my people a moment''s respite from the naga threat.', 21154),
(109269, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\INV_Misc_Bell_01:20|tA %s has been alerted to your presence!', '|TInterface\\Icons\\INV_Misc_Bell_01:20|tA %s has been alerted to your presence!', 21154),
(109270, 'ruRU', '|TInterface\\Icons\\INV_Misc_Bell_01:20|tAn alarm has been sounded! A reinforcement has entered the fray!', '|TInterface\\Icons\\INV_Misc_Bell_01:20|tAn alarm has been sounded! A reinforcement has entered the fray!', 21154),
(109271, 'ruRU', 'The boy-king serves at the master''s table. Three lies will he offer you.', '', 21154),
(109272, 'ruRU', 'Her heart is a crater, and we have filled it.', '', 21154),
(109273, 'ruRU', 'The king of diamonds has been made a pawn.', '', 21154),
(109274, 'ruRU', 'At the hour of her third death, she ushers in our coming.', '', 21154),
(109275, 'ruRU', 'From the earth, he draws strength. Our earth. Our strength.', '', 21154),
(109276, 'ruRU', 'Its surface blazes bright, masking shadows below.', '', 21154),
(109277, 'ruRU', '', 'Thanks, now its time for some payback!', 21154),
(109278, 'ruRU', 'To find him, drown yourself in the circle of stars.', '', 21154),
(109279, 'ruRU', 'Four keys to open our way. Four torches to light our path.', '', 21154),
(109280, 'ruRU', 'Flesh is his gift. He is your true creator.', '', 21154),
(109281, 'ruRU', 'The lord of ravens will turn the key.', '', 21154),
(109283, 'ruRU', 'Hmph... Someone will notice I am missing! They will come looking for me!', 'Hmph... Someone will notice I am missing! They will come looking for me!', 21154),
(109284, 'ruRU', 'I will start the ritual at your command.$B$BThe twins won''t take too kindly to being summoned, so be prepared for a fight.$B$Once they are weakened, use the Bloodstone to enslave them.$B$BAre you ready to begin?', '', 21154),
(109285, 'ruRU', '', 'True. You will have to make an appearance.', 21154),
(109286, 'ruRU', '', 'Use the Bloodstone!', 21154),
(109287, 'ruRU', 'Welcome to Mornath''s Manor of Mystery! I have all manner of mysterious curios from before and after the Sundering.', '', 21154),
(109288, 'ruRU', 'He insists that you return it, and that I may use force if necessary.', 'He insists that you return it, and that I may use force if necessary.', 21154),
(109289, 'ruRU', '', 'Friend, the withered are relentless in their attacks on our whelplands. They''ve left our captive young starving for mana!', 21154),
(109290, 'ruRU', '', 'Take back the mana crystals the withered stole and use them to revive the whelplings. Move quickly, friend!', 21154),
(109291, 'ruRU', '', 'Your actions have ensured a future for the blue dragons in Azsuna. With the withered''s threat subsided, you''ve given us the time we need to recover.', 21154),
(109292, 'ruRU', 'How brave of you, $n.', 'How brave of you, $n.', 21154),
(109293, 'ruRU', 'I owe you a debt of gratitude.', 'I owe you a debt of gratitude.', 21154),
(109294, 'ruRU', 'These bandages... thank you.', 'These bandages... thank you.', 21154),
(109295, 'ruRU', 'I... I must get back to battle!', 'I... I must get back to battle!', 21154),
(109296, 'ruRU', 'A little shaken, but I''ll be alright.', 'A little shaken, but I''ll be alright.', 21154),
(109297, 'ruRU', 'For the Alliance!', 'For the Alliance!', 21154),
(109298, 'ruRU', '', 'You will join the eternal hunt!', 21154),
(109299, 'ruRU', 'Ah yes, the heroes have arrived. So persistent. So confident. But your arrogance will be your undoing!', '', 21154),
(109300, 'ruRU', 'Have you forgotten your humiliation on the Broken Shore? How your precious high king was bent and broken before me? Will you beg for your lives as he did, whimpering like some worthless dog?', '', 21154),
(109301, 'ruRU', 'Have you forgotten your humiliation on the Broken Shore? How your mighty warchief was stuck in the belly like a helpless piglet? Will you die slowly as he did, consumed by fel corruption and squealing for a merciful end?', '', 21154),
(109302, 'ruRU', 'Your pathetic Alliance will fall to dust. Your new boy-king will bow down and serve me... as will all of you!', '', 21154),
(109303, 'ruRU', 'Your pathetic Horde will fall to dust. In the end, death will inherit this world and she will be waiting.', '', 21154),
(109304, 'ruRU', 'The husk of Illidan will prove an ideal vessel for my master''s glory. Sargeras will rise, and together we will watch your world burn!', '', 21154),
(109305, 'ruRU', '', 'None will defile the warlord''s hoard!', 21154),
(109306, 'ruRU', 'Let the endgame begin!', '', 21154),
(109307, 'ruRU', 'You will not stop the ritual!', '', 21154),
(109308, 'ruRU', 'The vessel must be made ready!', '', 21154),
(109309, 'ruRU', 'One by one you fall!', '', 21154),
(109310, 'ruRU', 'You should have bent the knee!', '', 21154),
(109311, 'ruRU', 'Surrender! I may yet show mercy!', '', 21154),
(109312, 'ruRU', 'Thus do the champions of this world fall!', '', 21154),
(109313, 'ruRU', 'No more distractions! I have work to do...', '', 21154),
(109314, 'ruRU', 'Come forth and serve me!', '', 21154),
(109315, 'ruRU', 'Strike for Sargeras!', '', 21154),
(109316, 'ruRU', 'Rid me of these pests!', '', 21154),
(109317, 'ruRU', 'Kill them in my master''s name!', '', 21154),
(109318, 'ruRU', 'I''ll make ashes of you!', '', 21154),
(109319, 'ruRU', 'You dare trespass at the heart of the Nightmare itself? Foolish mortals! Here, my will is absolute. Here, I am the master!', '', 21154),
(109320, 'ruRU', 'My will is unbreakable!', '', 21154),
(109321, 'ruRU', 'You''ll never escape my grasp!', '', 21154),
(109322, 'ruRU', 'Behold... power given form!', '', 21154),
(109323, 'ruRU', 'Drink in the glory!', '', 21154),
(109324, 'ruRU', 'Burn from within!', '', 21154),
(109325, 'ruRU', 'A taste of the master''s might!', '', 21154),
(109326, 'ruRU', 'The Nightmare has corrupted dragons, gods, and legends. Your downfall will be simple and swift!', '', 21154),
(109327, 'ruRU', 'Let the storm rain death upon you!', '', 21154),
(109328, 'ruRU', 'Never underestimate a master warlock!', '', 21154),
(109329, 'ruRU', 'Another dreamer for my Nightmare!', '', 21154),
(109330, 'ruRU', 'You failed, heroes! The ritual is upon us! But first, I''ll indulge myself a bit... and finish you!', '', 21154),
(109331, 'ruRU', 'You will never stir again!', '', 21154),
(109332, 'ruRU', 'Why won''t you die? Why do you keep resisting?', '', 21154),
(109333, 'ruRU', 'Eternal slumber! Eternal madness!', '', 21154),
(109334, 'ruRU', 'This fate awaits you all!', '', 21154),
(109335, 'ruRU', 'My victory draws near!', '', 21154),
(109336, 'ruRU', 'Your souls are mine, woven for all time into the fabric of the Nightmare!', '', 21154),
(109337, 'ruRU', 'That''s quite the distance! Must be some way to distract her castin''.', '', 21154),
(109338, 'ruRU', 'I will not fail you, master! More power... just need more power...', '', 21154),
(109339, 'ruRU', 'My victory is absolute. The power of Nightmare grows!', '', 21154),
(109340, 'ruRU', 'NO! I will not permit it!', '', 21154),
(109341, 'ruRU', 'They are mine, Ysera! You cannot save them!', '', 21154),
(109342, 'ruRU', 'Embrace the Dreaming, champions! It can save you!', '', 21154),
(109343, 'ruRU', 'Let the Dreaming wash away his darkness!', '', 21154),
(109344, 'ruRU', 'No more dreams! Only Nightmare!', '', 21154),
(109345, 'ruRU', 'Your respite is over! Awaken and face your doom!', '', 21154),
(109346, 'ruRU', 'My work... left... unfinished...', '', 21154),
(109347, 'ruRU', 'Nightmares are... never... forgotten...', '', 21154),
(109348, 'ruRU', 'I''ll slice into the heart of you!', '', 21154),
(109349, 'ruRU', 'I will sever you from the waking world!', '', 21154),
(109350, 'ruRU', 'Time to cut the last tether to your mortal life!', '', 21154),
(109351, 'ruRU', 'Feel the devastation of the Nightmare!', '', 21154),
(109352, 'ruRU', 'I''ll level you one by one!', '', 21154),
(109353, 'ruRU', 'Time to crush your dreams!', '', 21154),
(109354, 'ruRU', 'Succumb to the madness!', '', 21154),
(109355, 'ruRU', 'Give in to the Nightmare!', '', 21154),
(109356, 'ruRU', 'Your dreams are mine!', '', 21154),
(109357, 'ruRU', 'Your torment will be unending!', '', 21154),
(109358, 'ruRU', 'There is no escape!', '', 21154),
(109359, 'ruRU', 'Heroes! Champions! Step forth and hear me!', '', 21154),
(109360, 'ruRU', 'The Nightmare has long been a cancer eager to consume the Emerald Dream. Had Xavius succeeded, his corruption would have overwhelmed Azeroth, giving rise to a living Nightmare.', '', 21154),
(109361, 'ruRU', 'Your triumph restores the Dream and safeguards your world. The allies of Xavius will never relent, but this road, at least, is closed to them.', '', 21154),
(109362, 'ruRU', 'To honor your courage, I offer passage into the pure heart of the Dream. As you feel the essence of life blooming beneath your feet, know that it endures thanks to what you achieved this day.', '', 21154),
(109363, 'ruRU', 'Out of the rolling ocean I rise. The lord of tides has answered your call, Farseer of the Earthen Ring.', '', 21154),
(109364, 'ruRU', '', 'Heretic! I will slay you in Volund''s name!', 21154),
(109365, 'ruRU', 'The time has come to use the Idol of the Wilds and call upon the great god, Malorne. Never did I believe I would see the great ancient himself. This is a moment that we will speak of for ages to come.', '', 21154),
(109366, 'ruRU', 'I am ready to begin.', 'I am ready to begin.', 21154),
(109367, 'ruRU', 'My chosen will protect me for all eternity!', '', 21154),
(109368, 'ruRU', 'You are not worthy of Titanstrike''s might!', '', 21154),
(109369, 'ruRU', '', 'I grow tired of this, be consumed by the darkness!', 21154),
(109370, 'ruRU', '', 'It''s just you and me now, little priest! Your pathetic light won''t save you now!', 21154),
(109371, 'ruRU', '', 'It seems Garuhod''s recipe was incomplete. I think some bile might be needed to balance this out. I know it doesn''t taste great, but bear bile has amazing properties!', 21154),
(109372, 'ruRU', '', 'Fetch me some livers from the bears in the highlands. Only the fat ones, mind you! Oh, and some hippogryph eggs as well. A little variety can''t hurt.', 21154),
(109373, 'ruRU', '', 'Wonderful! I feel like we''re on the cusp of discovering the cure to this curse! Who would''ve thought that a lush like Garuhod might have held the key to our freedom?', 21154),
(109374, 'ruRU', '', 'What is that noise? Naranoth, you better not have another jailbreak or I''ll leave you on this pathetic rock to rot!', 21154),
(109375, 'ruRU', '', 'Are you truly stupid enough to think you can face me, an Eredar sorceress of the Burning Legion?', 21154),
(109376, 'ruRU', '', 'My darkness will consume you!', 21154),
(109377, 'ruRU', '', 'No! My staff is absorbing the light! Damn you, priest, and your accursed magic!', 21154),
(109378, 'ruRU', '', 'My staff is reacting to the light! Noooo!!', 21154),
(109379, 'ruRU', 'That must be it! The door''s glowin'' with the same energy as all of these spirits.', '', 21154),
(109380, 'ruRU', '', 'He dares to send someone in his stead? That accursed wretch. Listen, and I will tell you the truth about the man you serve.', 21154),
(109381, 'ruRU', '', 'I will dispel the runes. Protect me!', 21154),
(109382, 'ruRU', 'Will do, Prust!', '', 21154),
(109383, 'ruRU', '', 'Hold it right there!', 21154),
(109384, 'ruRU', '', 'You are unworthy of this place. Leave at once!', 21154),
(109385, 'ruRU', '', 'Merciful prophet! What is that!?', 21154),
(109386, 'ruRU', 'What are filthy mortals doing near the masters portal? I''ll rip the answer from your souls!', '', 21154),
(109387, 'ruRU', 'Salma! Where''s my Salma!?', '', 21154),
(109388, 'ruRU', '', 'My husband! Is he alright?', 21154),
(109389, 'ruRU', '', 'I will make this lake beautiful...', 21154),
(109390, 'ruRU', 'Do you even call this laboring? The master will have your hides!', '', 21154),
(109391, 'ruRU', 'If I catch you drinking the reagents again, I''ll turn you over to master!', '', 21154),
(109392, 'ruRU', 'Hello. Have you come to join the Empyrean Society of Exotic Magical Arts?', 'Hello. Have you come to join the Empyrean Society of Exotic Magical Arts?', 21154),
(109393, 'ruRU', 'That''s the spirit! One down, two to go!', '', 21154),
(109394, 'ruRU', '', 'They grow in strength. Prepare yourselves!', 21154),
(109395, 'ruRU', 'Look, the door''s opening!', '', 21154),
(109397, 'ruRU', 'Keep them from entering the chamber! The ritual is almost complete!', 'Keep them from entering the chamber! The ritual is almost complete!', 21154),
(109398, 'ruRU', '', 'You two can yell at each other later, it be time to get out of this place.', 21154),
(109399, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As an elemental shaman you commune with ancient spirits and command primal elemental forces. Your Flame Shock ability will set your enemies ablaze, burning them while you cast other spells.', '', 21154),
(109400, 'ruRU', 'Use Flame Shock on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109401, 'ruRU', 'Why stop with fire? Once your enemies are burning, you can hurl molten lava at them. Using Lava Burst while your enemies are affected by Flame Shock increases its damage.', '', 21154),
(109402, 'ruRU', 'Use Lava Burst on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109403, 'ruRU', 'Hurling lightning from your hands is your main weapon for overcoming enemies. Use Lightning Bolt whenever other abilities are not available.', '', 21154),
(109404, 'ruRU', 'Use Lightning Bolt on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109405, 'ruRU', 'Be wary, my friend- my magic is strong, but their constructs and commanders have proven much more difficult to dispatch. Choose your targets wisely.', '', 21154),
(109406, 'ruRU', 'Shaman of the Earthen Ring, let our powers combine!', '', 21154),
(109407, 'ruRU', 'We call upon Neptulon, the great Lord of Tides in the name of Azeroth!', '', 21154),
(109408, 'ruRU', '', 'I''ll help the others if it''s the last thing I do.', 21154),
(109409, 'ruRU', 'I need another invisibility spell applied.', 'I need another invisibility spell applied.', 21154),
(109410, 'ruRU', 'Hear our words and answer the call of the Earthen Ring!', '', 21154),
(109411, 'ruRU', 'I will prepare our forces to journey to Tirisfal. You can make your way there through the portal to the Dalaran Crater.', '', 21154),
