(109738, 'ruRU', 'Hmm, that is indeed interesting. We study exotic magic of all types in order to prepare ourselves for ascension.', 'Hmm, that is indeed interesting. We study exotic magic of all types in order to prepare ourselves for ascension.', 21154),
