(109741, 'ruRU', 'For the Horde!', '', 21154),
(109742, 'ruRU', 'In the end, though, he could not see Azshara''s treachery for what it was and an Eredar warlock claimed his life before the war was over.', 'In the end, though, he could not see Azshara''s treachery for what it was and an Eredar warlock claimed his life before the war was over.', 21154),
(109743, 'ruRU', 'I can still feel his legacy here, though...', 'I can still feel his legacy here, though...', 21154),
(109744, 'ruRU', 'A portion of your power can be coalesced into a Healthstone. If you take damage, ingest the Healthstone to recover health.', '', 21154),
(109745, 'ruRU', 'Once a place of much color and prosperity, it was second only to Zin-Azshari in grandeur. All but the Moon Guard thought it destroyed after the Sundering...', 'Once a place of much color and prosperity, it was second only to Zin-Azshari in grandeur. All but the Moon Guard thought it destroyed after the Sundering...', 21154),
(109746, 'ruRU', 'Use Create Healthstone.', '', 21154),
(109747, 'ruRU', 'Long have we looked out over the shield that protected our brothers and sisters. How such separation changed them...', 'Long have we looked out over the shield that protected our brothers and sisters. How such separation changed them...', 21154),
(109748, 'ruRU', 'Now, heal some of the damage you''ve taken with your Healthstone.', '', 21154),
(109749, 'ruRU', 'Now, heal some of the damage you''ve taken with your Healthstone.', '', 21154),
(109750, 'ruRU', 'A great many believed that he forged for himself a vessel to replace the sensation of the Well of Eternity during the War of the Ancients, but I do not know more than that.', 'A great many believed that he forged for himself a vessel to replace the sensation of the Well of Eternity during the War of the Ancients, but I do not know more than that.', 21154),
(109751, 'ruRU', 'You''re low on health, use your Healthstone!', '', 21154),
(109752, 'ruRU', 'A well-prepared warlock can survive almost anything... even death! Using your Soulstone ability preserves your very soul for later. Don''t worry, you weren''t using it anyway! With your soul stored, you can return from the dead at will.', '', 21154),
(109753, 'ruRU', 'Use Soulstone to survive death.', '', 21154),
(109754, 'ruRU', 'Astounding! I knew warlocks had this power, but it''s still impressive to see in action.', '', 21154),
(109755, 'ruRU', '', 'My gun... it''s jammed!', 21154),
(109756, 'ruRU', 'I would imagine if such a thing exists, it would be here. Hidden away somewhere significant to Latosius himself.', 'A great many believed that he forged for himself a vessel to replace the sensation of the Well of Eternity during the War of the Ancients, but I do not know more than that.', 21154),
(109757, 'ruRU', '', 'Careful! They''re stronger than they seem!', 21154),
(109758, 'ruRU', '', 'Looks like you could use some company.', 21154),
(109759, 'ruRU', '', 'You keep ''em at a distance. I''ll do the rest.', 21154),
(109760, 'ruRU', '', 'Be careful out here, $n. The air is full of their foul odor.', 21154),
(109761, 'ruRU', '', 'Not too familiar with these parts. I best keep on.', 21154),
(109762, 'ruRU', 'Oh, my, yes! This is going to yield so much exciting data!', '', 21154),
(109763, 'ruRU', 'I''m ready to get started.', 'I''m ready to get started.', 21154),
(109764, 'ruRU', 'Long have I watched over this place. To see it in such a state brings me great pain. I must know that those who remain will continue to look after the Amulet.', '', 21154),
(109765, 'ruRU', 'Go to the Arena, face my trial, and then I will show you where it is hidden.', '', 21154),
(109766, 'ruRU', 'Hear me, Moon Guard! You have resisted your demise so far. By order of the Grand Magistrix, this will not stand.', '', 21154),
(109767, 'ruRU', '', 'Thanks! I feel much better now!', 21154),
(109768, 'ruRU', 'To me! Let us show these inferior beings true power.', '', 21154),
(109769, 'ruRU', 'Thank you, friend, for restoring Cenarius to his natural state.  Our world has, once again, been saved through your deeds.', '', 21154),
(109770, 'ruRU', '', '%s gasps.', 21154),
(109771, 'ruRU', '', 'You need to leave, $c... NOW!', 21154),
(109772, 'ruRU', '<Wounded guy on the ground. Heal them up.>', '<Wounded guy on the ground. Heal them up.>', 21154),
(109773, 'ruRU', '', 'The demons are encroaching on our lands from Suramar. We must drive them back! If you take out their leaders, my Scalewardens will bring down their portals.', 21154),
