(109794, 'ruRU', '', 'Pity to waste wine, but it looked like a sour vintage anyway.', 21154),
(109795, 'ruRU', '', 'The local wildlife preys upon our injured whelplings. Please, protect them.', 21154),
(109796, 'ruRU', '', 'That whelp will recover in time. You have my thanks.', 21154),
(109797, 'ruRU', '', 'If you want to aid our cause, you''ll need to sharpen your skills. Meet with Melayl for training.', 21154),
(109798, 'ruRU', '', 'It seems you know your stuff. We may have a use for you.', 21154),
(109799, 'ruRU', '', 'I believe I may have discovered the secret of Garuhod''s recipe. I need you to gather some specific ingredients, but you must be careful. These creatures are most delicate!', 21154),
(109800, 'ruRU', '', 'Excellent! I''ll give the recipe a try. The real trick will be finding someone willing to drink it...', 21154),
(109801, 'ruRU', '', 'Don''t let the size of that brute fool you. He''s as dangerous as the rest of his kind. Watch out for his poison scales!', 21154),
