(109808, 'ruRU', 'While you are busy, Calydus will search for a suitable location for the ritual.', '', 21154),
(109809, 'ruRU', '', 'You did right by your fellow warlocks, which is commendable, and surprising. \n\nI know some who would choose the pursuit of power over the needs of others...', 21154),
(109810, 'ruRU', '', 'I escape one demon world, only to dwell within another demon world. \n\nAt least this one is under your control.', 21154),
(109811, 'ruRU', '', 'With the Dreadscar demons under your control, their power will be ours to dissect and command.', 21154),
(109812, 'ruRU', '<Zinnin bows his head slightly, silently acknowledging your presence.>', '', 21154),
(109813, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Arms warriors are the ultimate physical combatants, using martial skill and weaponry to crush those who stand against them. But you cannot defeat an opponent that''s out of reach. Fortunately, you have a skill to solve this problem.', '', 21154),
(109814, 'ruRU', 'Use your Charge ability to cover the distance to this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(109815, 'ruRU', 'Warriors don''t stroll up to face a foe! Use Charge to close the distance on your opponent. Try it!', '', 21154),
