(109841, 'ruRU', 'Use Whirlwind!', '', 21154),
(109842, 'ruRU', 'In the heat of battle there will be times you need to move quickly to avoid danger... or confront it! Heroic Leap allows you to bound across the battlefield to accomplish either goal.', '', 21154),
