(109844, 'ruRU', 'Use Eviscerate!', '', 21154),
(109846, 'ruRU', 'You''re in trouble! Use Vanish!', '', 21154),
(109847, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as an arms warrior.', '', 21154),
(109848, 'ruRU', 'In order to enact the failsafe ritual we will need to clear the room. Say the word and I will begin.', '', 21154),
(109849, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a subtlety rogue.', '', 21154),
(109851, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the fearlessness and ferocity of a warrior!', '', 21154),
(109852, 'ruRU', 'Show me you''ve got the stuff.', '', 21154),
(109853, 'ruRU', 'When you feel ready, explore your spellbook and the talent tree for additional abilities you can learn.', '', 21154),
(109854, 'ruRU', 'Whirlwind is not the only attack you can use against multiple enemies. Cleave allows you to attack several enemies that are in front of you. For every enemy hit, your next Whirlwind does additional damage!', '', 21154),
