(109864, 'ruRU', 'Use Crimson Vial to restore health!', '', 21154),
(109865, 'ruRU', 'A rogue''s reflexes are far superior to the average person. In times of extreme danger, a rogue can rely on these catlike reflexes to avoid almost any physical attack for a short time. Evasion can''t be used too often, so save it for emergencies.', '', 21154),
(109866, 'ruRU', 'Use Evasion to increase your chance to dodge incoming attacks.', '', 21154),
(109867, 'ruRU', 'There are times that you might want to close in on a target but not deal damage right away. By using Shadowstep, you will remain in stealth and be poised to strike.', '', 21154),
