(109901, 'ruRU', 'Your allies have fallen! %s retreats!', 'Your allies have fallen! %s retreats!', 21154),
(109902, 'ruRU', 'Shaman, you braved the tempest with a peaceful mind. Your focus inspires me. Go now, with my blessings upon you.', '', 21154),
(109903, 'ruRU', 'At last we can begin. Now we will need to move quickly once the ritual is complete, it will close this tomb permanently once the hammer is in our possession.', '', 21154),
(109904, 'ruRU', 'Something is wrong. One of the globes isn''t working! Blast!', '', 21154),
(109905, 'ruRU', 'It must have been taken, perhaps by one of the crazed monsters. It can only be below and we need it. Whenever you are ready, champion.', '', 21154),
(109906, 'ruRU', 'Somehow they must have knocked it loose and taken it below. We must venture further into the depths and find it or this has all been for naught.', '', 21154),
(109907, 'ruRU', 'Our whelplings hunger for the flesh of the moose, but the young ones cannot stomach it raw. Plunge this lightning rod into fresh corpses and our whelps shall do the rest.', '', 21154),
(109908, 'ruRU', 'Our whelps will grow strong gorging upon the feast you provided. You have our thanks.', '', 21154),
(109909, 'ruRU', 'You have heard of the War of the Ancients, I am sure. If you are to listen to the Highmountain tauren, they were responsible for defeating Tichondrius.\n\nBut they had help. Much help indeed. Will you listen to my story?', '', 21154),
(109910, 'ruRU', 'Honorless murlocs have overtaken the village of Morheim. I cannot abide their presence in that once-sacred place. Eradicate this filth!', '', 21154),
(109911, 'ruRU', 'Well done. I remember the one whom this village owes its name. He was a fine leader.', '', 21154),
(109912, 'ruRU', 'Esara, you really don''t want to join the Empyrean Society.', '', 21154),
(109913, 'ruRU', '', 'I don''t? Why not?', 21154),
(109914, 'ruRU', 'Their methods are a bit...distasteful. Besides, the Tirisgarde are much more powerful! We could use a mage with your experience.', '', 21154),
(109915, 'ruRU', 'Look. $n has arrived!', '', 21154),
(109916, 'ruRU', 'The children of Mimiron have crafted a clever toy they claim can harness the power of the storm. Go forth and test their handiwork in battle.', '', 21154),
(109917, 'ruRU', 'A most amusing device. But cleverness is useless without strength of arms!', '', 21154),
(109918, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Discipline priests draw upon the opposing forces of Light and Shadow, choosing when to heal and when to inflict damage. Shadow Word: Pain taints your foes with shadow energy, wounding them slowly over time.', '', 21154),
