(109950, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a windwalker monk you use your fists and your speed to overcome enemies. This builds up Chi, a resource that allows you to unleash your most powerful attacks. Start by using your primary attack, Tiger Palm, to deal damage and generate Chi.', '', 21154),
