(110036, 'ruRU', 'Paralyze the soldier who attacks you.', '', 21154),
(110037, 'ruRU', 'Fights aren''t always fair... or are they? If you find yourself facing three or more opponents, tap your inner spirit to duplicate yourself, making you your own ally! Your allied selves will attack enemies automatically.', '', 21154),
