(110054, 'ruRU', 'Our ascension is at hand. Have you brought us something worthy?', 'Our ascension is at hand. Have you brought us something worthy?', 21154),
(110055, 'ruRU', 'Once you''ve ambushed your prey, it''s time to weaken them. Rake will cause your target to bleed, wounding them over time. Your Shred ability also deals extra damage to bleeding targets, so these are great abilities to use together.', '', 21154),
