(110069, 'ruRU', 'You have 5 combo points! Use Rip!', '', 21154),
(110070, 'ruRU', 'Use Rip!', '', 21154),
(110071, 'ruRU', 'Ever needed to quickly get out of a sticky situation? Druids excel at doing this. Dash increases your movement speed significantly for a short time. It can''t be used often, so save it for when you really need it.', '', 21154),
(110072, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Dash to increase your movement speed.', '', 21154),
(110073, 'ruRU', 'As a druid you also have the ability to call on the powers of nature for a variety of other abilities, like healing! After you''ve taken damage, use Healing Touch to restore your health.', '', 21154),
