(110075, 'ruRU', 'Heal yourself with Healing Touch!', '', 21154),
(110076, 'ruRU', 'Using spells will usually pull you out of shapeshift forms. Don''t forget to return to cat form for combat.', '', 21154),
(110077, 'ruRU', 'Use Cat Form.', '', 21154),
(110078, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you need an enemy to stay put so you can close the distance to them... or make a hasty retreat. Entangling Roots will cause plant roots to spring from the ground and hold the target in place for a short time.', '', 21154),
