(110543, 'ruRU', 'Use Survival Instincts to reduce incoming damage.', '', 21154),
(110544, 'ruRU', 'When in Cat Form you can rely on the instincts of an animal to help pull you through a tough fight. Survival Instincts reduces incoming damage for a short time. Save it for when you really need it!', '', 21154),
(110545, 'ruRU', 'Use Entangling Roots to root my soldier to the ground.', '', 21154),
(110546, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you need an enemy to stay put so you can close the distance to them... or make a hasty retreat. Entangling Roots will cause plant roots to spring from the ground and hold the target in place for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110547, 'ruRU', 'Use Rip on the target dummy with five combo points.', '', 21154),
(110548, 'ruRU', 'Tougher enemies may require a diverse set of abilities to overcome. As an alternative to Ferocious Bite, Rip can be used to deal bleeding damage over time to your target, and is a good ability to spend combo points on early in a fight. Like Ferocious Bite, Rip is a finishing move, and is best used when you have 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(110549, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger''s Fury to restore some energy and then attack the target dummy with Shred.', '', 21154),
(110550, 'ruRU', 'Most of your attacks require energy to use. You might find yourself low on energy at times, rendering you unable to use any abilities. Tiger''s Fury restores some energy and also increases your damage for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110551, 'ruRU', 'Rake inflicts its damage over time, so you don''t need to use it again until your target is no longer affected by it.', '', 21154),
(110552, 'ruRU', 'Use Rake on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110553, 'ruRU', 'Once you''ve ambushed your prey, it''s time to weaken them. Rake will cause your target to bleed, wounding them over time. Your Shred ability also deals extra damage to bleeding targets, so these are great abilities to use together.', '', 21154),
(110554, 'ruRU', 'When you have 5 combo points, use Ferocious Bite on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110555, 'ruRU', 'Both your Shred and Rake abilities generate combo points which can fuel powerful finishing moves. Ferocious Bite is a finishing move that deals increased damage the more combo points you have. Try to use it when you have a full 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(110556, 'ruRU', 'Use Shred on the target dummy from stealth, then use it once to deal damage out of stealth.', '', 21154),
(110557, 'ruRU', 'Your primary attack is Shred. Though powerful on its own, using Shred from stealth increases its damage, so try to start a fight while you are in stealth.', '', 21154),
(110558, 'ruRU', 'Stealth lasts until you cancel it, attack, or take damage.', '', 21154),
(110559, 'ruRU', 'Use Prowl to enter stealth.', '', 21154),
(110560, 'ruRU', 'As a cat you can move with uncanny stealth, allowing you to approach your enemies undetected. Prowl puts you in stealth mode.', '', 21154),
(110561, 'ruRU', 'Use Cat Form and assume the form of a cat.', '', 21154),
(110562, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a feral druid your main weapon is shapeshifting. In Cat Form, your claws and fangs rip and bleed your opponents. Soon they''ll be weak enough for you to go for the throat with a mighty finishing move. Use Cat Form to become a cat.', '', 21154),
(110563, 'ruRU', 'Use Feign Death to trick my soldier into stopping his attack.', '', 21154),
(110564, 'ruRU', 'Even the greatest hunters sometimes find themselves in over their heads. When facing certain defeat, use Feign Death to trick your enemies into thinking you''re no longer a threat.', '', 21154),
(110565, 'ruRU', 'Use Multishot to dispatch all the enemies.', '', 21154),
(110566, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you''ll find yourself outnumbered. A skilled hunter can unleash destruction upon a host of adversaries at once! Multi-shot allows you to fire a spread of projectiles hitting several enemies near your target. Using this attack causes your pet to cleave multiple enemies as well.', '', 21154),
(110567, 'ruRU', 'Your pet has died! When this happens, your Mend Pet ability changes to Revive Pet, which will bring your faithful companion back to life.', '', 21154),
(110568, 'ruRU', 'Use Mend Pet to heal your pet.', '', 21154),
(110569, 'ruRU', 'Your pet has been wounded! Fortunately, you can aid your trusty companion. Mend Pet will allow you to heal damage your pet has taken.', '', 21154),
(110570, 'ruRU', 'Use Kill Command multiple times on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110571, 'ruRU', 'Sending your pet to attack and distract an enemy gives you more time to line up your ranged attacks. Don''t worry, your pet is resilient! Using Kill Command will cause your pet to perform a strong attack, and is also a great way to initiate a fight.', '', 21154),
(110572, 'ruRU', 'Use Call Pet to bring your pet to battle.', '', 21154),
(110573, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Beast master hunters possess a deep bond with their pets, calling and bolstering them in battle while striking at foes with ranged attacks. Alongside your trusty pet, you are the master of your environment. Summon Pet will call your pet to your side.', '', 21154),
(110574, 'ruRU', 'Use Multi-Shot to damage multiple enemies at once!', '', 21154),
(110575, 'ruRU', 'Your pet is hurt! Use Mend Pet!', '', 21154),
(110576, 'ruRU', 'Use Kill Command!', '', 21154),
(110577, 'ruRU', 'Kill Command is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(110578, 'ruRU', 'Use Dire Beast!', '', 21154),
(110579, 'ruRU', 'Dire Beast is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(110580, 'ruRU', 'Use Cobra Shot!', '', 21154),
(110581, 'ruRU', 'Call your pet!', '', 21154),
(110582, 'ruRU', 'Use Bestial Wrath!', '', 21154),
(110583, 'ruRU', 'Bestial Wrath is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(110584, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a beast master hunter.', '', 21154),
(110585, 'ruRU', 'Prove to me you have all the skill and cunning of a hunter!', '', 21154),
(110586, 'ruRU', 'Use Bestial Wrath while attacking the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110587, 'ruRU', 'When in combat, Bestial Wrath sends you and your pet into a frenzy of rage that increases your damage for a short time.  While under its effects, using Dire Beast will shorten the time before you can trigger Bestial Wrath again.', '', 21154),
(110588, 'ruRU', 'Use Cobra Shot on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110589, 'ruRU', 'I''m sure you''re ready to join in on the action. Cobra Shot is your primary ranged attack, pummeling your enemy while your pet keeps their attention.', '', 21154),
(110590, 'ruRU', 'Use Dire Beast on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110591, 'ruRU', 'Now let''s see what other forces of nature you command. Dire Beast will allow you to summon a nearby beast to join the fight and attack your target for a short time.', '', 21154),
(110592, 'ruRU', 'Use Blizzard to dispatch this group of enemies.', '', 21154),
(110593, 'ruRU', 'Mages are masters of dealing damage to many enemies at once. You can pelt a target location with shards of ice by using a potent spell called Blizzard. Great name, don''t you think?', '', 21154),
(110594, 'ruRU', 'Remember that Ice Lance does extra damage to frozen targets, so using Frost Nova and Ice Lance together is a powerful tactic.', '', 21154),
(110595, 'ruRU', 'Freeze this enemy using Frost Nova.', '', 21154),
(110596, 'ruRU', 'What if you could freeze foes in their tracks, preventing them from even reaching you? Frost Nova freezes nearby enemies in place, allowing you to move away and destroy them safely. For now, let''s just practice freezing them in place.', '', 21154),
(110597, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Blink.', '', 21154),
(110598, 'ruRU', 'The battlefield can be a dangerous place, so moving about is crucial to your survival. But using your legs is so mundane! Fortunately, you have a spell that befits a master of the magical arts. Blink allows you to teleport a short distance to avoid danger or close in on an enemy.', '', 21154),
(110599, 'ruRU', 'Your Water Elemental has died. Cast Summon Water Elemental to call it back!', '', 21154),
(110600, 'ruRU', 'You''re in trouble! Use Invisibility!', '', 21154),
(110601, 'ruRU', 'Wait until you have Fingers of Frost, or your target is frozen, to use Ice Lance.', '', 21154),
(110602, 'ruRU', 'Your target is frozen! Use Ice Lance!', '', 21154),
(110603, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance!', '', 21154),
(110604, 'ruRU', 'Fingers of Frost has triggered! Use Ice Lance now!', '', 21154),
(110605, 'ruRU', 'You''re taking damage! Cast Ice Barrier!', '', 21154),
(110606, 'ruRU', 'Use Frozen Orb!', '', 21154),
(110607, 'ruRU', 'Frozen Orb is available! Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110608, 'ruRU', 'Use Frostbolt!', '', 21154),
(110609, 'ruRU', 'Use Frost Nova!', '', 21154),
(110610, 'ruRU', 'You need to freeze your enemy in place before they reach you.', '', 21154),
(110611, 'ruRU', 'You''re under attack! Use Frost Nova to immobilize your opponent!', '', 21154),
(110612, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies. Try casting Blizzard!', '', 21154),
(110613, 'ruRU', 'Use Invisibility to escape combat.', '', 21154),
(110614, 'ruRU', 'Need to get out of a fight in a hurry? Invisibility is a great spell for getting out of a sticky situation. Use it and enemies will be unable to target you, letting you escape form combat. But be careful! It doesn''t last long.', '', 21154),
(110615, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Barrier to reduce incoming damage.', '', 21154),
(110616, 'ruRU', 'Despite your best efforts, you may not be able to prevent an enemy from reaching you. In those cases, a little bit of extra protection is needed. Ice Barrier creates a shield of ice to absorb enemy attacks.', '', 21154),
(110617, 'ruRU', 'Use Frostbolt on the target dummy until Fingers of Frost is triggered, then use Ice Lance.', '', 21154),
(110618, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance on the target dummy while the Fingers of Frost effect is active.', '', 21154),
(110619, 'ruRU', 'There is one more way that Ice Lance can be used to maximize its power. Frostbolt occasionally triggers the Fingers of Frost effect, which gives a huge boost to Ice Lance damage. Let''s test it out.', '', 21154),
(110620, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance on the frozen target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110621, 'ruRU', 'But Ice Lance''s real power lies in using it against a frozen target, which greatly increases its damage.', '', 21154),
(110622, 'ruRU', 'Use Ice Lance on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110623, 'ruRU', 'Now we''ll take a look at Ice Lance. It''s similar to Frostbolt, but can be cast instantly, albeit for less damage.', '', 21154),
(110624, 'ruRU', 'Use Frozen Orb on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110625, 'ruRU', 'Another potent spell you can wield is Frozen Orb. Cast this spell whenever it is available, as it can make your Ice Lance more powerful. Be careful, though, as it hits all enemies in its path, not just your target.', '', 21154),
(110626, 'ruRU', 'Use Frostbolt on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110627, 'ruRU', 'Your most fundamental and reliable attack is Frostbolt. This long-range attack will damage and slow your enemies, and has a chance to empower other attacks.', '', 21154),
(110628, 'ruRU', 'Use Summon Water Elemental to summon your pet.', '', 21154),
(110629, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a frost mage you excel at controlling the battlefield by freezing enemies in place as ice and hail pummel them into submission. Frost Mages can call forth a water elemental pet, so we''ll start there.', '', 21154),
(110630, 'ruRU', 'Use Effuse to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(110631, 'ruRU', 'Taking damage is part of battle, but as a monk you can tap the spiritual mists to heal yourself or an ally. Use Effuse to heal your wounds.', '', 21154),
(110632, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Roll a few times.', '', 21154),
(110633, 'ruRU', 'Monks are fast and agile, able to zip around the battlefield at will. The primary ability that gives monks their mobility is Roll, which causes you to quickly roll a good distance in whatever direction you are moving.', '', 21154),
(110634, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger Palm!', '', 21154),
(110635, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger Palm to generate Chi!', '', 21154),
(110636, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies! Try using Storm, Earth, and Fire!', '', 21154),
(110637, 'ruRU', 'Roll, monk, roll!', '', 21154),
(110638, 'ruRU', 'Use Rising Sun Kick!', '', 21154),
(110639, 'ruRU', 'Rising Sun Kick is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(110640, 'ruRU', 'Use Flying Serpent Kick a second time to stop your movement early.', '', 21154),
(110641, 'ruRU', 'Use Fists of Fury!', '', 21154),
(110642, 'ruRU', 'Fists of Fury is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(110643, 'ruRU', 'Heal yourself with Effuse!', '', 21154),
(110644, 'ruRU', 'You have maximum Chi! Use Blackout Kick!', '', 21154),
(110645, 'ruRU', 'Use Blackout Kick!', '', 21154),
(110646, 'ruRU', 'Use Touch of Death on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110647, 'ruRU', 'Your monk training has taught you the precision necessary to strike an enemy''s pressure points. Touch of Death deals massive damage, but takes a short time to take effect. Use it whenever you meet someone you don''t like, although you might want to save it for your toughest enemies!', '', 21154),
(110648, 'ruRU', 'Use Storm, Earth, and Fire to attack all three of these target dummies at once.', '', 21154),
(110649, 'ruRU', 'Fights aren''t always fair... or are they? If you find yourself facing three or more opponents, tap your inner spirit to duplicate yourself, making you your own ally! Your allied selves will attack enemies automatically.', '', 21154),
(110650, 'ruRU', 'Paralyze the soldier who attacks you.', '', 21154),
(110651, 'ruRU', 'Sometimes you might get in over your head, facing more enemies than you can handle. Take one enemy out of the fight by paralyzing him! Paralyze will knock out an enemy for a short time, but the foe will recover if he takes any damage.', '', 21154),
(110652, 'ruRU', 'Use Flying Serpent Kick to travel to the target dummy and damage it.', '', 21154),
(110653, 'ruRU', 'Roll is not your only ability for mobility. Windwalker monks can also launch themselves through the air, flying at their targets. Use Flying Serpent Kick to launch yourself at your enemy. Using it a second time while you are in the air will end your flight and deal damage to enemies nearby.', '', 21154),
(110654, 'ruRU', 'Use Fists of Fury on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110655, 'ruRU', 'You have an abundance of attacks at your disposal, windwalker! Fists of Fury costs 3 Chi and does a lot of damage. It will also hit additional enemies near your target. Use Fists of Fury whenever it''s available, or if you face multiple enemies.', '', 21154),
(110656, 'ruRU', 'Use Blackout Kick on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110657, 'ruRU', 'While not as powerful as Rising Sun Kick, your Blackout Kick still packs a punch... or, uh, a kick! It hits much harder than Tiger Palm, so use Blackout Kick to spend your extra Chi.', '', 21154),
(110658, 'ruRU', 'Use Rising Sun Kick on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110659, 'ruRU', 'Starting combat with Tiger Palm gives you enough Chi to unleash the powerful Rising Sun Kick, an attack that uses 2 Chi and deals substantial damage. Use it whenever it is available.', '', 21154),
(110660, 'ruRU', 'Use Tiger Palm on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110661, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a windwalker monk you use your fists and your speed to overcome enemies. This builds up Chi, a resource that allows you to unleash your most powerful attacks. Start by using your primary attack, Tiger Palm, to deal damage and generate Chi.', '', 21154),
(110662, 'ruRU', 'Use Flash of Light until all your health is restored.', '', 21154),
(110663, 'ruRU', 'Divine Shield protected you from the mage''s first attack, but the second attack has left you wounded. As a paladin your conviction allows you to heal yourself and your allies. Flash of Light is a cornerstone of your healing arsenal.', '', 21154),
(110664, 'ruRU', 'Divine Shield will completely protect you from all attacks for a short period of time, so save it for emergencies.', '', 21154),
(110665, 'ruRU', 'Use Divine Shield to make yourself temporarily invulnerable to all damage!', '', 21154),
(110666, 'ruRU', 'Paladins face many dangerous situations, and preparation can be the key to your survival. Divine Shield prevents incoming attacks from harming you.', '', 21154),
(110667, 'ruRU', 'You''re at maximum Holy Power already! Use Templar''s Verdict!', '', 21154),
(110668, 'ruRU', 'Use Templar''s Verdict!', '', 21154),
(110669, 'ruRU', 'Templar''s Verdict is available! Use it now!', '', 21154),
(110670, 'ruRU', 'Cast Judgment!', '', 21154),
(110671, 'ruRU', 'Judgment is available!  Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110672, 'ruRU', 'Judgment is a ranged ability. Try using it from further away!', '', 21154),
(110673, 'ruRU', 'Use Flash of Light to heal yourself!', '', 21154),
(110674, 'ruRU', 'Use Divine Shield!', '', 21154),
(110675, 'ruRU', 'You''re in trouble! Cast Divine Shield to save yourself!', '', 21154),
(110676, 'ruRU', 'Use Crusader Strike!', '', 21154),
(110677, 'ruRU', 'Use Crusader Strike to generate Holy Power!', '', 21154),
(110678, 'ruRU', 'Cast Blade of Justice!', '', 21154),
(110679, 'ruRU', 'Blade of Justice is available!  Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110680, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a retribution paladin.', '', 21154),
(110681, 'ruRU', 'Show me you fight with the courage and zeal of a paladin!', '', 21154),
(110682, 'ruRU', 'Build up Holy Power by using your attacks, then use Templar''s Verdict on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110683, 'ruRU', 'Using Blade of Justice and Crusader Strike in combat builds up Holy Power. Unleash this divine magic through Templar''s Verdict, a powerful melee attack that infuses your weapon with the strength of the Light.', '', 21154),
(110684, 'ruRU', 'Use Crusader Strike on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110685, 'ruRU', 'Blade of Justice is an excellent tool to deal damage as your opponent approaches. Once your foe has closed to striking range, unleash your weapon using Crusader Strike.', '', 21154),
(110686, 'ruRU', 'Use Blade of Justice on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110687, 'ruRU', 'Judgment can be used on enemies at a distance or up close whenever it is available. As your enemy closes in, unleash a potent mid-range attack called Blade of Justice.', '', 21154),
(110688, 'ruRU', 'Use Judgment on this target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110689, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. As a retribution paladin you are a stalwart protector of the weak, a bringer of punishment to the unjust! Your attacks are a mix of ranged spells and melee that build up and unleash Holy Power. Your devotion to the Light empowers you to hurl a mighty hammer of Judgment at your foes.', '', 21154),
(110690, 'ruRU', 'Yes, sign me up for the rumble!', 'Yes, sign me up for the rumble!', 21154),
(110691, 'ruRU', 'Use Plea to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(110692, 'ruRU', 'You''ve taken damage, but this presents no problem for a priest. The Light gives you the power to restore the health of yourself or your allies.', '', 21154),
(110693, 'ruRU', 'Use Psychic Scream to prevent this group of enemies from hitting you.', '', 21154),
(110694, 'ruRU', 'Well done! In some battles you will face multiple opponents at the same time. Fortunately, you are not defenseless in such cases. Psychic Scream terrifies nearby opponents, causing them to run away in fear.', '', 21154),
(110695, 'ruRU', 'Use Power Word: Shield to prevent taking damage from this enemy.', '', 21154),
(110696, 'ruRU', 'As a priest you have many ways to protect and restore health. One of your most useful defensive abilities is Power Word: Shield, which absorbs all damage from attacks when active. Always remember to maintain your shield during fights.', '', 21154),
(110697, 'ruRU', 'Cast Smite!', '', 21154),
(110698, 'ruRU', 'There''s no need to recast Shadow Word: Pain when the previous one still has lots of time left on it.', '', 21154),
(110699, 'ruRU', 'Cast Shadow Word: Pain!', '', 21154),
(110700, 'ruRU', 'Shadow Word: Pain has expired on your target, cast it again!', '', 21154),
(110701, 'ruRU', 'Use Psychic Scream to cause fear to your enemies!', '', 21154),
(110702, 'ruRU', 'Cast Power Word: Shield to protect yourself!', '', 21154),
(110703, 'ruRU', 'Use Plea to heal yourself!', '', 21154),
(110704, 'ruRU', 'Cast Penance now!', '', 21154),
(110705, 'ruRU', 'Penance is available!  Cast it now!', '', 21154),
(110706, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a discipline priest.', '', 21154),
(110707, 'ruRU', 'Command the forces of Shadow and Light to achieve victory!', '', 21154),
(110708, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadowmend to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(110709, 'ruRU', 'Healing can also be provided by the Shadow, but it comes at a cost. Shadowmend is a very powerful heal, but part of that healing will drain away over time.', '', 21154),
(110710, 'ruRU', 'Use Power Word: Barrier to protect these soldiers.', '', 21154),
(110711, 'ruRU', 'You are not limited to only shielding yourself or an ally. A priest can also cast a shield over an entire area, protecting all allies within its boundaries.', '', 21154),
(110712, 'ruRU', 'Use Smite on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110713, 'ruRU', 'The power of the Light allows you to Smite any enemy that stands before you! It is your most frequently used damage spell, best used when Penance is not available.', '', 21154),
(110714, 'ruRU', 'Use Penance on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110715, 'ruRU', 'The Light is a formidable ally, capable of restoring your friends or striking down foes. Penance is a potent spell that deals damage to your enemies. Use Penance whenever it is available.', '', 21154),
(110716, 'ruRU', 'Your target is now afflicted with shadow damage. Use Shadow Word: Pain whenever your target is not already affected by it.', '', 21154),
(110717, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadow Word: Pain on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110718, 'ruRU', 'Welcome, $p. Discipline priests draw upon the opposing forces of Light and Shadow, choosing when to heal and when to inflict damage. Shadow Word: Pain taints your foes with shadow energy, wounding them slowly over time.', '', 21154),
(110719, 'ruRU', 'Use Vanish to evade this brute.', '', 21154),
(110720, 'ruRU', 'There''s just one last thing you need to learn. Sometimes a strategic retreat is necessary so you can live to fight another day. Vanish allows you to disengage from combat and make a quick getaway.', '', 21154),
(110721, 'ruRU', 'Shadowstrike to a target, generate 5 combo points with Backstab, and finish them with Eviscerate. That should leave you in stealth, ready to Shadowstrike to your next target.', '', 21154),
(110722, 'ruRU', 'You''re learning how to paint with a dagger. Now it''s time to perfect your art.', '', 21154),
(110723, 'ruRU', 'You''re in trouble! Use Vanish!', '', 21154),
(110724, 'ruRU', 'Use Backstab to generate combo points.', '', 21154),
(110725, 'ruRU', 'Starting combat from stealth is more effective.', '', 21154),
(110726, 'ruRU', 'You''re facing multiple enemies, try using Shuriken Storm!', '', 21154),
(110727, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadowstrike!', '', 21154),
(110728, 'ruRU', 'Use Nightblade!', '', 21154),
(110729, 'ruRU', 'You have 5 combo points. Use Nightblade!', '', 21154),
(110730, 'ruRU', 'Wait until you have 5 combo points to use Nightblade!', '', 21154),
(110731, 'ruRU', 'Use Eviscerate!', '', 21154),
(110732, 'ruRU', 'You have 5 Combo Points. Use Eviscerate!', '', 21154),
(110733, 'ruRU', 'Wait until you have 5 combo points to use Eviscerate!', '', 21154),
(110734, 'ruRU', 'Use Crimson Vial to restore health!', '', 21154),
(110735, 'ruRU', 'Use Backstab!', '', 21154),
(110736, 'ruRU', 'Use Backstab to generate combo points.', '', 21154),
(110737, 'ruRU', 'Well done, $p! You are now prepared to do battle as a subtlety rogue.', '', 21154),
(110738, 'ruRU', 'Show me you''ve got the stuff.', '', 21154),
(110739, 'ruRU', 'Practice using Sprint to increase your movement speed.', '', 21154),
(110740, 'ruRU', 'Ever needed to get out of a sticky situation quickly? Rogues excel at doing this. Sprint increases your movement speed significantly for a short time, and can be used fairly frequently. I want to see you run, rogue!', '', 21154),
(110741, 'ruRU', 'Use Shuriken Storm to dispatch this group of enemies.', '', 21154),
(110742, 'ruRU', 'Enemies that try to surround you will be in for a nasty surprise! Shuriken Storm unleashes damage on all enemies circled around you. It will also generate a combo point for every enemy hit.', '', 21154),
(110743, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadowstep to appear behind a distant target.', '', 21154),
(110744, 'ruRU', 'There are times that you might want to close in on a target but not deal damage right away. By using Shadowstep, you will remain in stealth and be poised to strike.', '', 21154),
(110745, 'ruRU', 'Use Evasion to increase your chance to dodge incoming attacks.', '', 21154),
(110746, 'ruRU', 'A rogue''s reflexes are far superior to the average person. In times of extreme danger, a rogue can rely on these catlike reflexes to avoid almost any physical attack for a short time. Evasion can''t be used too often, so save it for emergencies.', '', 21154),
(110747, 'ruRU', 'Use Crimson Vial to restore some of your health.', '', 21154),
(110748, 'ruRU', 'You''ve taken some damage, but luckily a crafty rogue plans ahead. Crimson Vial is an alchemical concoction that will restore a portion of your health.', '', 21154),
(110749, 'ruRU', 'Use Nightblade with 5 combo points on the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110750, 'ruRU', 'Tougher enemies may require a broader range of abilities to overcome. As an alternative to Eviscerate, Nightblade can be used to deal damage over time to your target, and is a good ability to spend combo points on early in a fight. Like Eviscerate, Nightblade is a finishing move, and is best used when you have 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(110751, 'ruRU', 'Use Eviscerate with 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(110752, 'ruRU', 'Now that you''ve built up 5 combo points, it''s time to Eviscerate. Whenever you Eviscerate with 5 combo points, you will do massive damage and immediately enter stealth.', '', 21154),
(110753, 'ruRU', 'Use Shadowstrike to attack the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(110754, 'ruRU', 'Your deadliest attack from stealth is Shadowstrike. With Shadowstrike, you slip through the shadows to strike an enemy at a distance. Notice that certain abilities like Shadowstrike award combo points, which give extra damage you can unleash when the time is right.', '', 21154),
(110755, 'ruRU', 'Use Stealth to fade from view.', '', 21154),
(110756, 'ruRU', 'Rogues favor trickery and cunning. And what''s trickier than attacking before your target sees you coming? Stealth makes you invisible to most enemies. When in Stealth, you open up specialized tactics that can devastate foes.', '', 21154),
(110759, 'ruRU', 'Use Fire Elemental if you need a boost of damage in a fight!', '', 21154),
(110760, 'ruRU', 'As a shaman, you are able to coalesce primal elemental forces into physical form to aid you in battle.', '', 21154),
(110761, 'ruRU', 'Use Healing Surge to replenish your health to full.', '', 21154),
(110762, 'ruRU', 'You''ve taken damage, but this presents no problem for a shaman. Just as the elements can destroy, they also have the power to restore.', '', 21154),
(110763, 'ruRU', 'Use Chain Lightning against several enemies at once.', '', 21154),
(110764, 'ruRU', 'There are times you''ll face multiple opponents on the battlefield. Fortunately, you have a potent ability called Chain Lightning. When you strike an enemy with Chain Lightning, it jumps to additional foes near your target, damaging all of them.', '', 21154),
(110765, 'ruRU', 'Turn this soldier into a frog!', '', 21154),
