(110958, 'ruRU', 'Thanks!', 'Thanks!', 21154),
(110959, 'ruRU', 'Hati! That poor wolf took the brunt of it. Is she...?', '', 21154),
(110960, 'ruRU', 'She''s alive, but only barely. It appears she absorbed Titanstrike''s power to protect us from the explosion. It''s killing her!', '', 21154),
(110961, 'ruRU', 'Erase everything and try again', 'Erase everything and try again', 21154),
(110962, 'ruRU', 'Even though she''s a creature of lightning magic, her body can''t contain that much energy. My science can''t help her. I fear the Thunderspark''s power is soon to be lost.', '', 21154),
(110963, 'ruRU', '', 'Playtime''s over, mortal!', 21154),
(110964, 'ruRU', '', '$n, is that Felo''melorn? THE Felo''melorn, undying flame of the Sunstriders? The last time I saw that blade, it was in the hands of Prince Kael''thas, before the third war.', 21154),
(110965, 'ruRU', 'I know your heart aches at Hati''s loss, just as mine does, $p. You have a kinship with the spirits of wild creatures greater than any I have seen before.', '', 21154),
