(111653, 'ruRU', '<The shadowy figure glimmers in the corner of your eye like a shade from a forgotten time. He does not react to your presence.>', '<The shadowy figure glimmers in the corner of your eye like a shade from a forgotten time. She does not react to your presence.>', 21154),
(111654, 'ruRU', 'Yes, I am Lorin.', '', 21154),
(111655, 'ruRU', '', 'Nar''thala vas manari...', 21154),
(111656, 'ruRU', 'It was a little careless for you to come up here with no other pretense, but it cannot be helped.', '', 21154),
(111657, 'ruRU', 'I will join you and Cyrille when the time comes. You must now seek out Sylessa. She trains with the Commander to the North.', '', 21154),
(111658, 'ruRU', 'Hurry along before we are spotted together.', '', 21154),
(111659, 'ruRU', 'Rrrgghhh...', '', 21154),
(111660, 'ruRU', '', 'I''ve been looking all over for you, have you found... oh no...', 21154),
(111661, 'ruRU', 'RrrggaaAAHHGGHH!! RAAGGGHH!', '', 21154),
(111662, 'ruRU', '', 'This hunger... this fear...', 21154),
(111663, 'ruRU', '', 'The day he was exiled...', 21154),
(111664, 'ruRU', '', 'I know this...', 21154),
(111665, 'ruRU', 'Unnngh...', '', 21154),
(111666, 'ruRU', '<A ghostly figure rests on the stairway, a half-remembered shade from another time. He recognizes the staff you carry and nods towards you, grimly.>\n\nYou haven''t changed your mind, Alodi? It doesn''t trouble you that we''re pouring all of our energy into that staff of yours?', '', 21154),
(111667, 'ruRU', '', 'Such confusion... such rage... I-', 21154),
(111668, 'ruRU', '', 'Thalyssra! Are you alright?', 21154),
(111669, 'ruRU', 'I seek the wisdom of the council.', 'I seek the wisdom of the council.', 21154),
(111670, 'ruRU', 'Very well, mage. I will do as you ask... but please, be careful. No mortal has ever possessed such power.', '', 21154),
(111671, 'ruRU', '', 'I am truly sorry for your friend, he looks crushed. What could have...', 21154),
(111672, 'ruRU', 'Leave this area! Loken''s curse forces me to slay the allies of Tyr. Until he comes to collect Tyr''s essence, I must defend it!', '', 21154),
(111673, 'ruRU', '', 'He has never been aggressive before, perhaps we should leave. What say you?', 21154),
(111674, 'ruRU', '', 'I can see there is more going on here than I understand. What are you doing, $n?', 21154),
(111675, 'ruRU', 'I was sent here to find Galford, he had a relic of Tyr when he came here. Now Jotun has it. I need the relic to claim Tyr''s warhammer, will you help me?', 'I was sent here to find Galford, he had a relic of Tyr when he came here. Now Jotun has it. I need the relic to claim Tyr''s warhammer, will you help me?', 21154),
(111676, 'ruRU', '', 'Tyr''s warhammer? I do not know if I can face a titan keeper, but with your help, I will try!', 21154),
(111677, 'ruRU', '<The gnome flickers in the corner of your consciousness, a half-remembered shade from another time. His face lights up when he sees the staff in your hands.>\n\nIs it time, Alodi? Is your staff ready?', '', 21154),
(111678, 'ruRU', 'That''s all I''ve got, old friend. The Legion won''t know what hit ''em!', '', 21154),
(111679, 'ruRU', 'I just read an interesting paper on the lowly kobold. Apparently, these creatures are more fierce than their visual affordance might suggest.', '', 21154),
(111680, 'ruRU', 'Fetch me a reference on kobolds. I''d like to verify this hypothesis.', '', 21154),
(111681, 'ruRU', 'Fascinating.', '', 21154),
(111682, 'ruRU', 'Of course, a more pressing concern to our academy is the constant encroachment of the skrogs.', '', 21154),
(111683, 'ruRU', 'Unfortunately, I''m afraid that our library suffers a scarcity of information on these creatures.', '', 21154),
(111684, 'ruRU', 'Find me a book on skrogs. Anything will do.', '', 21154),
(111685, 'ruRU', 'Lastly, I''d like to brush up on dragons. Blue dragons, to be precise.', '', 21154),
(111686, 'ruRU', '<Is that... a dragon, languidly resting atop the greenhouse? The creature is there, and simultaneously not. She seems to be a memory from your staff, Ebonchill, and not part of this world. A draconic advisor from a forgotten time.>', '', 21154),
(111687, 'ruRU', 'We are currently on good terms with our northerly neighbors, but should our friendship wither, it can''t hurt to know how they fight.', '', 21154),
(111688, 'ruRU', '<You see a great blue dragon, resting languidly atop the greenhouse. She seems to be a memory from your staff, Ebonchill, and not part of this world. To your surprise, the mighty creature turns to face you, speaking slowly:>$b$bThe great Alodi returns, seeking ever more power. Tell me, mage, has the Council considered the impact of granting so much magical energy to a single mortal, hmmmm?$b$bAnd what if their beloved Guardian should ever betray them?$b$bI will be watching you...', '', 21154),
(111689, 'ruRU', 'I heard the spy is here and he''s very good looking.', 'I heard the spy is here and he''s very good looking.', 21154),
(111690, 'ruRU', 'It seems like there are some new faces here at tonight''s party...', 'It seems like there are some new faces here at tonight''s party...', 21154),
(111691, 'ruRU', 'Hmm, now I''ve heard a juicy rumor about the party. I heard there''s a Burning Legion spy here, making sure we''re still loyal!', 'Hmm, now I''ve heard a juicy rumor about the party. I heard there''s a Burning Legion spy here, making sure we''re still loyal!', 21154),
(111692, 'ruRU', 'The one that Elisande invited to the party? Now I didn''t say this, but that one is really a spy for the Burning Legion.', 'The one that Elisande invited to the party? Now I didn''t say this, but that one is really a spy for the Burning Legion.', 21154),
(111693, 'ruRU', 'Some are saying there''s a member of the Burning Legion attending this party incognito...', 'Some are saying there''s a member of the Burning Legion attending this party incognito...', 21154),
