(111729, 'ruRU', 'The pain. I am free... for the moment.', '', 21154),
(111730, 'ruRU', 'Loken''s enchantment won''t let me die, we only have a moment before I must continue Loken''s aggression.', '', 21154),
(111731, 'ruRU', 'Here, the spark. Take it and flee. I know my friend is dead, keep his memory alive.', '', 21154),
