(112690, 'ruRU', 'Easily defeated but in large numbers deadly. Perhaps something that hits a little harder?', '', 21154),
(112691, 'ruRU', 'Assassination rogues weaken their enemies before finishing them off. The best way to start a fight is with Garrote, a debilitating bleeding attack that causes your enemy to take damage over time.', '', 21154),
