(112693, 'ruRU', 'Always remember to use Garrote to keep your enemies bleeding.', '', 21154),
(112694, 'ruRU', 'Your main attack is called Mutilate. It deals damage as well as generating combo points that can used for powerful finishing moves.', '', 21154),
(112695, 'ruRU', 'Use Mutilate to attack the target dummy.', '', 21154),
(112696, 'ruRU', 'Now that you''ve built up 5 combo points, it''s time to use Rupture. Whenever you use Rupture with 5 combo points, you will do a strong bleeding attack that damages enemies over time.', '', 21154),
(112697, 'ruRU', 'Use Rupture with 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(112698, 'ruRU', 'I expected no less from someone acquainted with crippling ice magic. But how about something as skilled in spellcasting as yourself?', '', 21154),
(112699, 'ruRU', 'Rupture is not your only finishing move. If your target is already affected by Rupture, then using Envenom with 5 combo points deals good damage and maximizes the effect of your poisons.', '', 21154),
(112700, 'ruRU', 'Use Envenom with 5 combo points.', '', 21154),
(112701, 'ruRU', 'Well done, but Balaadur has been hunting mages for longer most have lived. You must be ready to use all of your abilities to face him.', '', 21154),
(112702, 'ruRU', 'For the final piece of the puzzle, a simple stone. A stone from Balaadur''s personal realm, left here by accident on one of his many ambushes.', '', 21154),
(112703, 'ruRU', 'There''s just one last thing you need to learn. Sometimes a strategic retreat is necessary so you can live to fight another day. Vanish allows you to disengage from combat and make a quick getaway.', '', 21154),
